ProgramUnit.Name: POPULATE_A_GROUP
ProgramUnit.ProgramUnitText:
PROCEDURE populate_a_group (p_group_name VARCHAR2)
IS
 lr_Grp recordgroup;
 ln_Count NUMBER;
 ls_RecGrp_Query VARCHAR2 (600);
BEGIN
 lr_Grp := Find_Group (p_group_name);

 IF NOT Id_Null (lr_Grp) THEN
 Delete_Group (lr_Grp);
 END IF;

 IF p_group_name = 'DATA_SUPPLIER' THEN
 ls_RecGrp_Query := 'select data_supplier_name rlabel, data_supplier rvalue 
 from data_supplier';
 ELSIF p_group_name = 'PROCESSING_CYCLE' THEN
 ls_RecGrp_Query :=
 'select unique to_char(processing_cycle) rlabel,to_char(processing_cycle) rvalue from pl_tld_airport
 where data_supplier = (select data_supplier from data_supplier where data_supplier = '''
 || :REP_BLK.DATA_SUPPLIER
 || ''') order by 1 desc';
 END IF;

 lr_Grp := Create_Group_From_Query (p_group_name, ls_RecGrp_Query);
 ln_Count := Populate_Group (lr_Grp);
 Populate_List ('REP_BLK.' || p_group_name, lr_Grp);

 IF Get_Group_Row_Count (lr_Grp) > 0 THEN
 COPY (Get_Group_Char_Cell (p_group_name || '.rvalue', 1),'REP_BLK.' || p_group_name);
 END IF;
END;

PACKAGE BODY EXPORT_CSV IS
 
 PROCEDURE Create_File_On_Server(file_handle out client_text_io.file_type) IS
 l_server_path VARCHAR2(4000);
 l_file_nm VARCHAR2(20) := 'sel_criteria_rep';
 l_srv_file_sep CHAR(1) := '/';
 pl_id ParamList;
-- l_File_Handle Client_Text_IO.file_type;
 --the_conn_str VARCHAR2(200) := GET_APPLICATION_PROPERTY(USERNAME)||'/'||GET_APPLICATION_PROPERTY(PASSWORD)||'@'||GET_APPLICATION_PROPERTY(CONNECT_STRING); 
 BEGIN
 --if :global.g_file_name is null then --Fix SCR 7493 16-JUN-2017
 if :REP_BLK.TYPE = 'Y' THEN
 :global.g_file_name := 'C:\'||'STD_APTS_ASSCT_WITH_APT_GRP_'||:REP_BLK.Processing_Cycle||'.csv';
 else
 :global.g_file_name := 'C:\'||'STD_APTS_NOT_ASSCT_WITH_APT_GRP_'||:REP_BLK.Processing_Cycle||'.csv';
 end if; 
 --end if; --Fix SCR 7493 16-JUN-2017
 if :global.g_delimiter is null then
 :global.g_delimiter := ',';
 end if;
 if :global.g_cancel is null then
 :global.g_cancel := 'TRUE';
 end if;
 
 pl_id := Get_Parameter_List('tempdata');
 IF NOT Id_Null(pl_id) THEN 
 Destroy_Parameter_List(pl_id); 
 END IF; 
 pl_id := Create_Parameter_List('tempdata'); 
 
 Add_Parameter(pl_id, 'G_FILE_NAME',TEXT_PARAMETER,:global.g_file_name); 
 Add_Parameter(pl_id, 'G_DELIMITER',TEXT_PARAMETER,:global.g_delimiter);
 Add_Parameter(pl_id, 'G_CANCEL',TEXT_PARAMETER,:global.g_cancel); 
 call_form('export_destination',NO_HIDE,NO_REPLACE,NO_QUERY_ONLY,SHARE_LIBRARY_DATA, pl_id); 
 --call_form('EXPORT_DEST',NO_HIDE,NO_REPLACE,NO_QUERY_ONLY,SHARE_LIBRARY_DATA);

 if :global.g_cancel = 'FALSE' then
 --till here 22may2017
 --File_Handle := Client_Text_IO.fopen(l_data_file_path, 'W'); --commented on 22may 2017
 File_Handle := client_text_io.fopen(:global.g_file_name, 'W');
 end if; --22MAY2017
 END Create_File_On_Server; 
 
 PROCEDURE Export_File IS
 l_sel_cnt VARCHAR2(4000);
 l_count NUMBER;
 v_value VARCHAR2(200) := NULL;
 Prev_S_Seq NUMBER;
 l_rec_count NUMBER(10) := 0;
 v_file_handle client_text_io.file_type;
 CURSOR Sel_Apt_cur is
 SELECT distinct --STD.*, 
 SBAG.Group_Name,
 NAV.NavDB_ID,
 NAV.Data_Supplier,
 Include_Exclude_Ind,
 STD.Airport_Ident,
 STD.Airport_Icao,
 Production_Ready_Ind,
 Primary_Focal
 FROM SELECT_BY_AIRPORT_GROUP SBAG, 
 AIRPORT_TO_SELECT ATS, 
 NAVDB NAV,
 PL_TLD_AIRPORT TLD, 
 PL_STD_AIRPORT STD
 WHERE SBAG.Select_by_ID = ATS.Select_by_ID
 AND NAV.NavDB_ID = SBAG.NavDB_ID
 AND NAV.NavDB_ID = TLD.Customer_Ident
 AND TLD.Airport_Ident = ATS.Airport_Ident
 --AND TLD.Airport_Icao = ATS.Airport_Icao
 AND STD.Airport_Ident = TLD.Airport_Ident
 --AND STD.Airport_Icao = TLD.Airport_Icao
 AND TLD.Data_Supplier = STD.Data_Supplier
 AND TLD.Data_Supplier = NAV.Data_Supplier
 AND TLD.Processing_Cycle = STD.Processing_Cycle
 AND STD.Processing_Cycle = :REP_BLK.Processing_Cycle
 AND STD.Data_Supplier = :REP_BLK.Data_Supplier 
 ORDER BY STD.Airport_Ident,STD.Airport_Icao,Group_Name;
 
 CURSOR NotSel_Apt_cur is
 SELECT DISTINCT N.NavDB_ID,
 N.Data_Supplier,
 S.Airport_Ident Std_Airport_Ident,
 S.Airport_Icao Std_Airport_Icao, 
 T.Airport_Ident Tld_Airport_Ident, 
 T.Airport_Icao Tld_Airport_Icao, 
 Production_Ready_Ind, 
 Primary_Focal 
 FROM PL_STD_AIRPORT S, 
 PL_TLD_AIRPORT T, 
 NavDB N
 WHERE S.Airport_Ident = T.Airport_Ident
 --AND S.Airport_Icao = T.Airport_Icao
 AND S.Processing_Cycle = T.Processing_Cycle
 AND S.Data_Supplier = T.Data_Supplier
 AND S.Data_Supplier = N.Data_Supplier
 AND T.Customer_Ident = N.navdb_id
 AND S.Data_Supplier = :REP_BLK.Data_Supplier
 AND S.Processing_Cycle = :REP_BLK.Processing_Cycle
 AND S.Airport_Ident--,S.Airport_Icao) 
 NOT IN ( SELECT STD.Airport_Ident
 --STD.Airport_Icao
 FROM SELECT_BY_AIRPORT_GROUP SBAG, 
 AIRPORT_TO_SELECT ATS, 
 NAVDB NAV,
 PL_TLD_AIRPORT TLD, 
 PL_STD_AIRPORT STD
 WHERE SBAG.Select_By_ID = ATS.Select_By_ID
 AND NAV.NavDB_ID = SBAG.NavDB_ID
 AND NAV.NavDB_ID = TLD.Customer_Ident
 AND TLD.Airport_Ident = ATS.Airport_Ident
 --AND TLD.Airport_Icao = ATS.Airport_Icao
 AND TLD.Data_Supplier = STD.Data_Supplier
 AND TLD.Data_Supplier = NAV.Data_Supplier
 AND TLD.processing_cycle = STD.processing_cycle
 AND STD.Airport_Ident = TLD.Airport_Ident
 --AND STD.Airport_Icao = TLD.Airport_Icao
 AND STD.Processing_Cycle = :REP_BLK.Processing_Cycle
 AND STD.Data_Supplier = :REP_BLK.Data_Supplier
 ) 
 ORDER BY 3,4; 
 ls_primary_focal varchar2(100):=NULL; 
 ls_focal_first_name varchar2(100);
 --v_rec_hdr varchar2(300):= NULL;
 BEGIN
 l_rec_count := 0;
 IF :REP_BLK.TYPE = 'Y' THEN
 FOR rec in Sel_Apt_cur
 LOOP
 l_rec_count := l_rec_count + 1;
 IF l_rec_count = 1 THEN 
 Create_File_On_Server(v_file_handle);
 IF :global.g_cancel = 'FALSE' THEN
 client_text_io.PUT_LINE(v_file_handle,'Exported on '||SYSDATE);
 client_text_io.PUT_LINE(v_file_handle,' ');
 client_text_io.PUT_LINE (v_file_handle,'S.No,NavDB ID,Data Supplier,Airport Ident,Airport Icao,Group Name,Inc/Exc Ind,Prod Ready Ind,Primary Focal');
 --Begin Fix SCR 7493 16JUN2017
 IF rec.Primary_Focal IS NOT NULL THEN
 BEGIN
 SELECT DECODE(LAST_NAME,NULL,FIRST_NAME,FIRST_NAME||' '||LAST_NAME ),FIRST_NAME --rlabel,LOGON_ID rvalue, logon_id
 INTO ls_primary_focal,ls_focal_first_name
 FROM COREPT_USER
 WHERE LOGON_ID = rec.Primary_Focal;
 EXCEPTION
 WHEN OTHERS THEN
 ls_primary_focal := rec.Primary_Focal;
 END; 
 IF ls_primary_focal IS NULL THEN
 ls_primary_focal := rec.Primary_Focal;
 END IF;
 END IF; 
 client_text_io.PUT_LINE (v_file_handle,l_rec_count||','||rec.NavDB_ID||','||rec.Data_Supplier||','||rec.airport_ident||','||rec.airport_icao||','||rec.group_name||','||rec.Include_Exclude_Ind||','||rec.Production_ready_Ind||','||ls_primary_focal);
 ls_primary_focal := NULL;
 -- Till here SCR 7493 16JUN2017
 ELSE
 EXIT;
 END IF; 
 ELSIF l_rec_count > 1 THEN
 IF rec.Primary_Focal IS NOT NULL THEN
 BEGIN
 SELECT DECODE(LAST_NAME,NULL,FIRST_NAME,FIRST_NAME||' '||LAST_NAME ),FIRST_NAME --rlabel,LOGON_ID rvalue, logon_id
 INTO ls_primary_focal,ls_focal_first_name
 FROM COREPT_USER
 WHERE LOGON_ID = rec.Primary_Focal;
 EXCEPTION
 WHEN OTHERS THEN
 ls_primary_focal := rec.Primary_Focal;
 END; 
 IF ls_primary_focal IS NULL THEN
 ls_primary_focal := rec.Primary_Focal;
 END IF;
 END IF; 
 client_text_io.PUT_LINE (v_file_handle,l_rec_count||','||rec.NavDB_ID||','||rec.Data_Supplier||','||rec.airport_ident||','||rec.airport_icao||','||rec.group_name||','||rec.Include_Exclude_Ind||','||rec.Production_ready_Ind||','||ls_primary_focal);
 ls_primary_focal := NULL;
 END IF;
 END LOOP;
 ELSE
 FOR rec1 in NotSel_Apt_cur
 LOOP
 l_rec_count := l_rec_count + 1;
 IF l_rec_count = 1 THEN 
 Create_File_On_Server(v_file_handle);
 IF :global.g_cancel = 'FALSE' THEN
 client_text_io.PUT_LINE(v_file_handle,'Exported on '||SYSDATE);
 client_text_io.PUT_LINE(v_file_handle,' ');
 client_text_io.PUT_LINE (v_file_handle,'S.No,NavDB ID,Data Supplier,TLD Airport Ident,TLD Airport Icao,STD Airport Ident,STD Airport Icao,Prod Ready Ind,Primary Focal');
 --Begin Fix SCR 7493 16062017
 IF rec1.Primary_Focal IS NOT NULL THEN
 BEGIN
 SELECT DECODE(LAST_NAME,NULL,FIRST_NAME,FIRST_NAME||' '||LAST_NAME ),FIRST_NAME --rlabel,LOGON_ID rvalue, logon_id
 INTO ls_primary_focal,ls_focal_first_name
 FROM COREPT_USER
 WHERE LOGON_ID = rec1.Primary_Focal;
 EXCEPTION
 WHEN OTHERS THEN
 ls_primary_focal := rec1.Primary_Focal;
 END; 
 IF ls_primary_focal IS NULL THEN
 ls_primary_focal := rec1.Primary_Focal;
 END IF; 
 END IF; 
 client_text_io.PUT_LINE (v_file_handle,l_rec_count||','||rec1.NavDB_ID||','||rec1.Data_Supplier||','||rec1.tld_airport_ident||','||rec1.tld_airport_icao||','||rec1.std_airport_ident||','||rec1.std_airport_icao||','||rec1.Production_ready_Ind||','||ls_Primary_Focal);
 ls_primary_focal := NULL;
 --End Fix SCR 7493 16062017 
 ELSE
 EXIT;
 END IF; 
 ELSIF l_rec_count > 1 THEN 
 IF rec1.Primary_Focal IS NOT NULL THEN
 BEGIN
 SELECT DECODE(LAST_NAME,NULL,FIRST_NAME,FIRST_NAME||' '||LAST_NAME ),FIRST_NAME --rlabel,LOGON_ID rvalue, logon_id
 INTO ls_primary_focal,ls_focal_first_name
 FROM COREPT_USER
 WHERE LOGON_ID = rec1.Primary_Focal;
 EXCEPTION
 WHEN OTHERS THEN
 ls_primary_focal := rec1.Primary_Focal;
 END; 
 IF ls_primary_focal IS NULL THEN
 ls_primary_focal := rec1.Primary_Focal;
 END IF; 
 END IF; 
 client_text_io.PUT_LINE (v_file_handle,l_rec_count||','||rec1.NavDB_ID||','||rec1.Data_Supplier||','||rec1.tld_airport_ident||','||rec1.tld_airport_icao||','||rec1.std_airport_ident||','||rec1.std_airport_icao||','||rec1.Production_ready_Ind||','||ls_Primary_Focal);
 ls_primary_focal := NULL;
 END IF;
 END LOOP;

 END IF;
 IF :global.g_cancel = 'TRUE' THEN
 NULL; 
 ELSIF l_rec_count = 0 and :REP_BLK.TYPE = 'Y' THEN
 dsp_msg('Report cannot be generated, there are no Airports exists which are Associated with Airport Groups');
 ELSIF l_rec_count = 0 and :REP_BLK.TYPE = 'N' THEN
 dsp_msg('Report cannot be generated, there are no Airports exists which are Not Associated with Airport Groups');
 ELSIF l_rec_count >= 1 THEN
 client_text_io.FClose (v_file_handle); 
 Message('Report generated Successfully.',No_Acknowledge);
 END IF; 
 END Export_File;
 
 END;
